> <br/> **Glimpse the Future.** The dragon has advantage on its 
<br/>    next attack roll, ability check, or saving throw.
> <br/> **Freeze Time (Costs 2 Actions).** A creature within 60 feet 
<br/>    that the dragon can see must make a DC 17 
<br/>    Charisma save. On a failure, they are paralyzed until 
<br/>    the end of the dragon's next turn. While paralyzed, 
<br/>    they are immune to all damage and effects.
